# Frontend

- Interactive elements: button semantics for actions, anchor+underline for content links.
- No hover-only interaction states.
- Font sizes: never below 14px body text on mobile.
- Grid: mobile-first, 2-col default, verify against IndustriesTaxonomyGrid.tsx pattern before introducing a new grid component.
